[dscrdvrsc] <Oink> @Crupti I just revisited the video and on minute 46 @Crypto Rich  asks: "*When Mainnet?*"
@miketout answers: "*I work my hardest to spend my time on actually building and creating and not trying to promise specific dates, because I care more that it's done right, than that it's done by a specific date.....*"
And in minute 48 Mike states: "*I do believe we are on the main net before the end of July, but I don't know that for sure and I really hesitate to give a specific date.*"
